genresAdvancedInfo.name: leipzig indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Leipzig indie is a subgenre of indie rock that originated in the city of Leipzig, Germany. It is characterized by its DIY ethos, experimental soundscapes, and introspective lyrics. Leipzig indie bands often incorporate elements of post-punk, shoegaze, and electronic music into their sound.
